rComments: Wrote the final exam on the rewrite date and was surprised to find that it was actually fair, unlike the midterm which was really hard so I was able to bring up my grade. The slides were straight from the textbook and read out by the lecturer, so you don't need to go to class. Just learn the examples from the book and tutorials.
Slides were from the textbook but the prof took time to answer questions outside class

If you're an international student like me and want to learn machine learning, GOOGLE ISLR and learn by yourself. It's free! Don't waste $5000 on this course. The prof purely just read through slides(can find on Youtube) and she doesn't seem to know the content of slides before she actually teaches us in the class. Trust me, Youtube is way better.

The professor even does not prepare well for the class. She has canceled the class just because she didn't prepare it in the last week. As a statistic professor, it is ridiculous that she does not know how to calculate the covariance in the class. Read book is better than attending to the class, since her slides are just copying from the textbook.

This is a brand new course... the prof mumbles when she speaks and just relies purely on the textbook to teach. She is knowledgeable, however does not explain the concepts very well. As well, I had to wait 3 weeks to get an assignment marked and the TA did not reply after 5 business days which is a very long time! DO NOT TAKE THIS COURSE AT ALL!!!
Legit just reads off the slides. Has a hard time working with quercus and the projector. STA314 is a terrible course
